{"data":[{"name":"84:1","price":"1. Quand le ciel sera lézardé,","arabic":"إِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ ٱنشَقَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5885,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:2","price":"2. et qu’il aura obéi à son Seigneur et accompli son devoir,","arabic":"وَأَذِنَتۡ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5886,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:3","price":"3. quand la terre sera aplanie,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡأَرۡضُ مُدَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5887,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:4","price":"4. qu’elle aura expulsé son contenu et s’en sera débarrassée,","arabic":"وَأَلۡقَتۡ مَا فِيهَا وَتَخَلَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5888,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:5","price":"5. et qu’elle aura obéi à son Seigneur et accompli son devoir,","arabic":"وَأَذِنَتۡ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5889,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:6","price":"6. alors, ô toi être humain qui sans cesse t’évertues pour aller vers ton Seigneur, (sache que) tu Le rencontreras !","arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِنَّكَ كَادِحٌ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ كَدۡحٗا فَمُلَٰقِيهِ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5890,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:7","price":"7. Celui qui aura reçu son Livre en sa main droite","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَنۡ أُوتِيَ كِتَٰبَهُۥ بِيَمِينِهِۦ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5891,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:8","price":"8. sera jugé d’un jugement clément,","arabic":"فَسَوۡفَ يُحَاسَبُ حِسَابٗا يَسِيرٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5892,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:9","price":"9. et s’en reviendra heureux auprès de sa famille.","arabic":"وَيَنقَلِبُ إِلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ مَسۡرُورٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5893,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:10","price":"10. Quant à celui qui recevra son Livre derrière son dos,","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ أُوتِيَ كِتَٰبَهُۥ وَرَآءَ ظَهۡرِهِۦ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5894,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:11","price":"11. il criera au malheur","arabic":"فَسَوۡفَ يَدۡعُواْ ثُبُورٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5895,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:12","price":"12. et brûlera dans le Brasier.","arabic":"وَيَصۡلَىٰ سَعِيرًا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5896,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:13","price":"13. Il était heureux auprès de sa famille,","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ فِيٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ مَسۡرُورًا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5897,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:14","price":"14. s’imaginant que jamais il ne reviendrait à la vie (pour être jugé).","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ ظَنَّ أَن لَّن يَحُورَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5898,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:15","price":"15. Eh bien si ! Son Seigneur, Tout Voyant, l’observait en permanence.","arabic":"بَلَىٰٓۚ إِنَّ رَبَّهُۥ كَانَ بِهِۦ بَصِيرٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5899,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:16","price":"16. J’en jure par le crépuscule !","arabic":"فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلشَّفَقِ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5900,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:17","price":"17. Par la nuit et ce qu’elle englobe !","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ وَمَا وَسَقَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5901,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:18","price":"18. Par la lune quand elle est pleine !","arabic":"وَٱلۡقَمَرِ إِذَا ٱتَّسَقَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5902,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:19","price":"19. Vous passerez sans cesse étape par étape.","arabic":"لَتَرۡكَبُنَّ طَبَقًا عَن طَبَقٖ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5903,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:20","price":"20. Pourquoi donc ne croient-ils pas ?","arabic":"فَمَا لَهُمۡ لَا يُؤۡمِنُونَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5904,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:21","price":"21. Et quand le Coran leur est lu ne se prosternent-ils pas ?[600]","arabic":"وَإِذَا قُرِئَ عَلَيۡهِمُ ٱلۡقُرۡءَانُ لَا يَسۡجُدُونَۤ۩","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5905,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[600] Une prosternation est recommandée après la lecture de ce verset.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:22","price":"22. C’est que les mécréants le tiennent pour mensonge.","arabic":"بَلِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ يُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5906,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:23","price":"23. Mais Allah Sait le mieux (les sentiments secrets) qu’ils nourrissent.","arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ أَعۡلَمُ بِمَا يُوعُونَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5907,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:24","price":"24. Annonce-leur donc un supplice très douloureux. ","arabic":"فَبَشِّرۡهُم بِعَذَابٍ أَلِيمٍ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5908,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"84:25","price":"25. À l’exception de ceux qui ont cru et ont accompli les bonnes œuvres, et qui auront alors une récompense illimitée.","arabic":"إِلَّا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ وَعَمِلُواْ ٱلصَّٰلِحَٰتِ لَهُمۡ أَجۡرٌ غَيۡرُ مَمۡنُونِۭ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5909,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"}],"chapter":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq","Chapter Al-Inshiqaq","Inshiqaq","Surah Inshiqaq","Chapter Inshiqaq","Al Inshiqaq","Surah Al Inshiqaq","Chapter Al Inshiqaq","Surah 84","Chapter 84","The Splitting Open","الإنشقاق"]}